cup down slowly on the saucer. The clink of porcelain was the only sound at the table for a moment.

161
00:14:41,330 --> 00:14:48,150
You owe $12,000 to the Costanza Brothers. He said. Neighborhood loan-sharking. You lost your job on Monday.

162
00:14:48,670 --> 00:14:53,690
